WEBVTT

02:59.280 --> 03:01.380
BROOKS: <i> Shall we start</i>
<i> with your earliest memory?</i>

03:06.720 --> 03:07.819
STONE: <i> The sea.</i>

03:10.558 --> 03:11.757
<i> Endless horizon,</i>

03:14.628 --> 03:15.761
<i> that was home.</i>

03:17.665 --> 03:18.830
BROOKS: <i> Anything else?</i>

04:19.560 --> 04:21.026
[SEAGULLS SQUAWKING]

05:01.435 --> 05:03.902
[SOBBING] Let me out!

05:13.380 --> 05:14.680
[GASPS]

05:15.416 --> 05:17.749
-[SCREAMS]
-[SHUSHES]

05:17.751 --> 05:18.884
BROOKS: Medical trials.

05:26.894 --> 05:30.329
So, are you interested?

05:32.900 --> 05:34.066
Doesn't that annoy you?

05:38.072 --> 05:39.438
I don't notice it.

05:41.475 --> 05:43.975
Does it annoy
you, Stone?

05:43.977 --> 05:45.811
All those hours
ticking away.

05:47.715 --> 05:49.681
You're just stuck in here
like the rest of us.

05:51.852 --> 05:53.585
Stalling tactics.

05:56.890 --> 05:59.658
I thought you'd
be more direct.

05:59.660 --> 06:01.893
What makes you think
I'd be more direct?

06:01.895 --> 06:04.463
If I was looking to stall,
I'd ask why it's
so dark in here.

06:06.900 --> 06:08.467
Diversion tactics.

06:09.803 --> 06:12.003
