round to me.

06:13.574 --> 06:14.773
Guessing the pills
are part of it.

06:18.011 --> 06:19.077
Headaches?

06:20.080 --> 06:22.013
That's none
of your concern.

06:22.015 --> 06:23.415
Maybe you're an addict.

06:24.084 --> 06:26.818
[STATIC BUZZING]

06:26.820 --> 06:29.054
Would you like to answer
my question, or not?

06:30.791 --> 06:32.824
Whatever your offer is,
the endgame's the same.

06:33.827 --> 06:36.862
There are no
underhand tactics.

06:36.864 --> 06:40.632
Replace the death penalty
with a full life sentence.

06:41.502 --> 06:44.035
-Simple.
-Simple?

06:47.141 --> 06:49.941
What an appealing offer.

06:49.943 --> 06:53.545
Life without parole.
See out my days
staring at metal bars.

06:54.715 --> 06:56.948
The answer is no.

06:56.950 --> 06:59.084
Are you saying
you want to die, Stone?

07:00.521 --> 07:04.055
Saying no the chance
of justice on the mainland?

07:04.057 --> 07:07.826
If a place like this can exist
off-borders, outside of the law,

07:07.828 --> 07:09.661
then there's no justice
for me anywhere.

07:10.631 --> 07:12.030
Thanks for the shallow
offer, though.

07:14.034 --> 07:17.068
You were in US
Special Forces

07:17.070 --> 07:21.506
and then a bodyguard
for the late State
Senator Alan.

07:22.709 --> 07:24.609
[FLUTTERING]

07:24.611 --> 07:27.546
