I killed Senator Alan,

07:41.495 --> 07:43.061
and then murdered
his wife and children.

07:45.032 --> 07:46.164
Are you saying
you didn't?

07:47.167 --> 07:49.685
Does it matter anymore?

07:49.686 --> 07:52.204
If, if you believe
you're innocent, you could
buy yourself some time.

07:52.206 --> 07:55.240
If I believe? Jesus.

07:58.645 --> 08:04.082
Your execution date
is set for next month.

08:04.084 --> 08:07.953
I'm offering you
your best chance
to get off this island,

08:07.955 --> 08:10.088
regardless of
what you think.

08:10.090 --> 08:14.526
You're outside the law here.
Outside society, forgotten.

08:16.864 --> 08:19.231
I'm giving you a chance
to turn things around.

08:21.602 --> 08:22.801
I've killed people.

08:23.837 --> 08:26.738
It was a job,
and it wasn't pleasant.

08:26.740 --> 08:29.741
The one time I protected
someone, I got hung out to dry.

08:29.743 --> 08:32.611
And I've ended up
out here, off-limits.

08:33.679 --> 08:35.013
